metadata.name: Rusted Saint ✦ 1
metadata.description:
Rusted Saints is a handmade portraits collection created by the artist Marcello Castellani. In them are glorified the beauty that is not ephemeral, the inner beauty that despite the passage of time it can never be destroyed. 

"Our bodies are dying day by day, 
our bodies rust day by day,
are you aware of it?
Your inner beauty is doing the opposite, 
day by day it is more luminous and shining.
Are you aware of it?
Open your eyes and realize it, 
otherwise, you will die without understanding the meaning."

MC
